            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_135gc' title='Col. 135GC &mdash; HL Deb 18 March 2002 vol 632 c135GC' name='column_135gc' href='#column_135gc' rel='bookmark'>135GC</a>
            should be made, except in these circumstances. That is what it means. I am talking about the English language now.
