          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0632P0-03725'>
        <a name='S5LV0632P0_20020318_GCR_36'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-muriel-turner' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0632P0_20020318_GCR_36' title='Link to this speech by Ms Muriel Turner' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
